{
  "stem": "10587.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I told him that I'm going to beat the hell out of him, and I did, yes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- and-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and since then, he would not participate.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had a radio towards the year-- I remember [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was the end of-- before the Germans came.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember having a radio.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we-- I did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we also had, besides the radio, we had a micro-- a gramophone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I used to always, especially during the war where our parents would not-- didn't let the kids go out at night, so friends and relatives would come to our apartment.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- and I would be given five pennies to keep it-- to-- I would crawl under the table and keep the gramophone-- I would wind it up constantly and replace-- and change the plates, the-- the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] record.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Right, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A lot of-- because they danced and they-- so a lot of [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] variety of music, I would say, a lot of the kind of music you can dance to.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some of it was even classical music, because we had a-- I remember the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] one tenor whose name was Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was quite-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the young people liked to listen to it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So I used to-- I was in charge of the microphone-- of the gramophone.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had a little radio which we would also listen to.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably more Jewish and whatever they were dancing in those days, maybe tango and [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] waltz or polka.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, that I experienced after.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we heard on the radio.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
